WEBVTT

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:04.000
Hello, friends. Welcome to this class.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:06.000
In this class, I want to show you how

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:10.000
you can edit a YouTube transcript with ChatGPT.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:13.000
In one of the videos I uploaded,

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:16.000
I showed you how you can edit a YouTube

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:18.000
transcript in Microsoft Word.

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Today, the focus of today's class is on how you

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:23.000
can make use of ChatGPT.

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:26.000
In the first part, we covered the transcript

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:28.000
without the timestamp.

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:31.000
So what you have to do is copy the transcript.

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:35.000
You can highlight it and copy the transcript.

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:39.000
Scroll down, press the Shift button on your left,

00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:43.000
and press this. Okay, copy.

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:46.000
Now, if you copy and paste the text

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:50.000
into a Word document,

00:00:50.000 --> 00:00:53.000
coming back to Home to adjust it

00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:56.000
is going to take a lot of time from you.

00:00:56.000 --> 00:00:57.000
If you want to save time,

00:00:57.000 --> 00:01:00.000
you want to leverage the use of artificial intelligence.

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:03.000
So what you have to do, instead of manual

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:06.000
arrangement,

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:09.000
especially when you have a large file,

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:11.000
which will take a lot of time,

00:01:11.000 --> 00:01:12.000
that's the heart of this video:

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:14.000
so that you can maximize the use

00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:17.000
of artificial intelligence.

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:21.000
So open ChatGPT. What you have to do is prompt it:

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:25.000
"Arrange the text," or a prompt that works for you.

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:26.000
Paste it.

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:30.000
Enter. Without much ado, you see that

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:33.000
ChatGPT has arranged the text.

00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:35.000
All you have to do is copy it.

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:40.000
You save your time. All you have to do is copy it.

00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:45.000
So, by the time it has arranged it,

00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:46.000
all you have to do is

00:01:46.000 --> 00:01:49.000
copy it into Microsoft Word.

00:01:49.000 --> 00:01:54.000
You can adjust it and use your desired font,

00:01:54.000 --> 00:01:56.000
and you can decide to compare and contrast.

00:01:56.000 --> 00:02:00.000
This is the transcript from YouTube.

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:04.000
You can view them side by side.

00:02:04.000 --> 00:02:07.000
Check it and compare.

00:02:07.000 --> 00:02:09.000
You see that it's the same text.

00:02:09.000 --> 00:02:14.000
You save your time, or you can decide to add other things.

00:02:14.000 --> 00:02:16.000
So this is how to use ChatGPT

00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:20.000
to edit a YouTube transcript.

00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:22.000
If you have yet to subscribe to this channel,

00:02:22.000 --> 00:02:24.000
you can hit the Subscribe button

00:02:24.000 --> 00:02:27.000
and also click the bell so that you can

00:02:27.000 --> 00:02:30.000
get alerts for subsequent uploads.

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:33.000
Thank you for watching.
